PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of RAYBURN DONALD DOUCETT, of Jacquet River, New Brunswick, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Export Development Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of John Chomiak, whose term has expired.
